cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM 

This paper deals with object detection for autonomous vehicles using multimodal sensor fusion, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV) and robotics (cs.RO). The proposed method also involves deep learning techniques, which are often discussed in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. Finally, the paper presents a new dataset, which falls under the multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category.
